{"tid":1698404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肥佬黎你同我出黎, 到底係唔係你條撚樣叫梁家傑瘋狂出國遊說外國勢力香港法治好好?","createTime":"2019-11-07T12:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T13:34:10.000Z","uid":31637,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"725e2f7827f1264e1eb7d91a5168d753ee14e4e5","tid":1698404,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:46:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母, 殺人魔警犯法冇事<br />\n被捕示威者被自殺<br />\n你同我講香港法治好撚好? 冇撚病下話<br />\n到底係唔係你個肥佬黎要梁家傑咁做<br />\n如果唔係, 咁肯撚定又係捐開獻金既果班大孖沙又發功啦屌"},{"pid":"1c50c13715d46a9f35fb7965d46d255f94366d3a","tid":1698404,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"含撚投票啦！永續社運，法治可守，革命不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadec77c5bf7604e674fd3095b519bd40594ff98","tid":1698404,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=20a1303f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"ae8a06cc5a1a3b75873f5b17d633cab214c0db93","tid":1698404,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"全香港出國遊說外國勢力香港法治冇問題次數最多既政黨<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公民黨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算唔撚係連登神探呀<br />\n都知道好撚有問題<br />\n有冇聽過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無事獻殷勤，非奸即盜</span></span><br />\n點解你公民黨呢大半年出國出得咁撚密, 次數密過全香港所有政黨加埋既總和"},{"pid":"a9da2a927a03dc1dd848fac84273f4a12103ca59","tid":1698404,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:06:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e948940a5c298c78ecd0b1e9a05c71c3441377aa","tid":1698404,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好你老母呀 仲有法治<br />\n15歲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}